A driver of a BMW X3
was shot and wounded on the M1 highway, between Jan Smuts Avenue and Empire
Road. According to social
activist Yusuf Abramjee the victims were followed from Fordsburg in
Johannesburg and robbed. Following that the M1 North was closed to traffic. Joburg Public Safety said The Johannesburg Metro Police
Department is diverting traffic off the freeway at Jan Smuts Avenue and Empire
road. In the video, one person can be seen lying on the highway, and
a Silver BMW 3 series is facing on-coming traffic. Several men could be seen taking out goods from the back of the
X3 and putting it in a Silver BMW 3 series.